snippet.title: Spell Slingers "Trick or Treat" Demo Trailer 01
snippet.description:
Find the Pumpkin King and TAKE HIS HEAD! 
https://honeycombinteractive.itch.io/spell-slingers-trick-or-treat-demo

FEATURES:
Open World Exploration!
Variety of Challenging AI Enemies!
11 unique Spells to Master!
Over 40 unique Armor, Wands, Items, and Accessories to Loot!
Gamepad/Controller Support (except menus)!
